1 NAME George /Washington/
2 GIVN George
2 SURN Washington
1 SEX M
1 TITL 1st President of the United States
1 BIRT
2 DATE 22 FEB 1732
2 PLAC Wakefield, Popes Creek, Westmoreland, Virginia
