1 BURI
2 PLAC Mount Vernon, Fairfax, Virginia
1 NOTE First Lady of the United States (1789-1797). Born Martha Dandridge,
2 CONT she first married Daniel Parke Custis in 1750 and had four children,
2 CONT two of whom survived infancy. After Custis died in 1757, she married
2 CONT George Washington in 1759. She was one of the wealthiest women in
2 CONT Virginia. She and George raised her grandchildren Nelly and George
2 CONT Washington Parke Custis at Mount Vernon.
